   <body>
      <prereq>
         <ul>
            <li>You must have <uicontrol>View</uicontrol> permission to view
a record.</li>
         </ul>
      </prereq>
      <context>
         <p>You can view the budget estimates records in the <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATES</uicontrol> list page.  </p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li href="../../../../Warehouse/Task_Warehouse/ProjplanNav.dita#task-1465/ProPlanNav">
            <p/>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the list page, double-click the required project.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the navigation pane, expand the project folder, expand <uicontrol>Budget Management</uicontrol>, and then click<uicontrol>Budget Estimates</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATES</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the list page, select the appropriate budget estimate record, and then click <uicontrol>View</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATE DETAILS</uicontrol> page is displayed. <fig>
                  <title>Budget Estimate Details Page</title>
                  <image href="../../../Icons/Screenshots_Icons/View_BdgtEstimate.jpg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATE DETAILS</uicontrol> page displays the following non-editable fields: </p>
            <p>
               <fig product="PG_Screenshot">
                  <title>Budget Estimate Details Page</title>
                  <image href="../../../Icons/Screenshots_Icons/View_BdgtEstimate.jpg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>The <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATE DETAILS</uicontrol> displays the following non-editable fields:</p>
            <p>
               <table colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="30%"/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="70%"/>
                     <thead>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Field Name</entry>
                           <entry>Description</entry>
                        </row>
                     </thead>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Budget Estimate ID</entry>
                           <entry>An automatically generated alphanumeric code that uniquely identifies the budget estimate.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>PWA Project Number</entry>
                           <entry>The project number for which the budget is  created.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Budget Estimate Name</entry>
                           <entry>The name of the budget estimate as received from EBS.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Project Name</entry>
                           <entry> The name of the associated project for which the budget is  created.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Budget Estimate Type</entry>
                           <entry>Displays <uicontrol>Work Order</uicontrol>.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Created Date</entry>
                           <entry>The date the budget estimate is created.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Measurement System</entry>
                           <entry>The  measurement system for the estimate.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Created By</entry>
                           <entry> Displays <uicontrol>Data Migration</uicontrol>.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Standard Item List</entry>
                           <entry>This field will appear blank.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Budget Template</entry>
                           <entry>This field will appear blank.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Description</entry>
                           <entry>The description of the budget estimate.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Estimate Total in $</entry>
                           <entry>Displays the  estimate amount of the project.</entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </p>
            <p>
               <fig product="PG_Screenshot">
                  <title>Budget Estimate Items Page</title>
                  <image href="../../../Icons/Screenshots_Icons/Bdgt_EstmteItems.jpg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>BUDGET ESTIMATE ITEMS</uicontrol> page displays the following non-editable fields:</p>
            <p>
               <table colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="30%"/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="70%"/>
                     <thead>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Column Name</entry>
                           <entry>Description</entry>
                        </row>
                     </thead>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Task Number</entry>
                           <entry>The number of the item received from EBS integration.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Line Number</entry>
                           <entry>The Mind assigned line number.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Task Name</entry>
                           <entry>The name of the item received from EBS integration.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Unit</entry>
                           <entry>The unit of measure for the project.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Quantity</entry>
                           <entry>The unit quantity of the defaulted as 1. </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Unit Price in $</entry>
                           <entry>The value is defaulted to 1.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Fund Rule</entry>
                           <entry>This field will appear blank. </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry>Amount in $</entry>
                           <entry>It is calculated as: Quantity * Unit Price.</entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
